title: [Herio] Tonari no Ayane-san
description:
There is a woman named Ayane living in the apartment next to mine.
She's elusive and quite the tease, often taunting me with provocative expressions.

One day, I forget the key to my apartment work, and am locked out of my room.
She happens upon me, and ends up offering that I stay the night in her place.

From there on out, we become VERY close neighbors indeed...
